metadata.name: Chalice Station Retention Medallion
metadata.description:
Retention 

This version represents the Retention of the Breath which is the most powerful aspect of the pranayama. It requires full expansion of the lungs and gives us so much information about the our lung capacity and respiratory health while allowing the blood to be fed with oxygen and rejuvenating the whole body with life giving prana. 

When you own an NFT from this series you get:  
- ChaliceStation.life Membership 
- Traditional Coconut Steam Chalice Kit  
- 365zing.com App subscription for 3 months  
- Premium All Glass Steam Chalice designed with unique custom cutchie by Jah9 (July Delivery)

As the owner of this “Retention” version you also:  
- Special Gift package of Power Plant Nutrition Wellness Products  
- Free Access to @CoinGod’s NFT Education Series  
- Custom special offering from 365Zing.com Wellness App  
- Future Value added
